gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Knicks 122, Bucks 109
gameRecap.excerpt: The Knicks defeated the Bucks, 122-109. Jalen Brunson led the Knicks with 43 points, six rebounds, and eight assists as Donte DiVincenzo added 26 points. Giannis Antetokounmpo (28 points, 15 rebounds, eight assists) and Damian Lillard (23 points, four rebounds, six assists) led the Bucks in the loss.
